txt.en: Thank you for contributing your collection! Please place your items in the box to receive your reward.
Wanted: Blackened skins from beasts near Amon Raith. Deliver the items to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith.
'These look as though they will do nicely. Thank you.'
'I am willing to fashion new packs for the people here, but I need some skins to tan and cure. Leather would be too heavy for people who may need to move quickly.'
DNT HIDING CONTENT - Task: Blackened Skins
Nathan Hodges, at Amon Raith, awaits the collection and delivery of blackened skins.
Deliver the blackened skins to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith
Wanted: Blackened skins from beasts near Amon Raith.
